# Remote Skills Manifest
#
# Skills listed here are downloaded from GitHub during install instead of being
# vendored in the dotfiles repo. Each non-blank, non-comment line has the form:
#
#   <skill-name>  <github-owner>/<repo>  <path-inside-repo>
#
# <path-inside-repo> is the directory that contains SKILL.md (and any other
# files the skill needs). The installer downloads the entire directory.
#
# To add a new marketplace skill, append a line here and re-run install.sh.

caveman  JuliusBrussee/caveman  skills/caveman
